1
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,960
Li Weihao.

2
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:06,680
Sorry.

3
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,000
Sorry.

4
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:13,160
Chao.

5
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,520
Sorry.

6
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,360
Chao.

7
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,980
