8
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,120
Morning.

9
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,080
Buying breakfast?

10
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:26,720
Brother.

11
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:28,380
