17
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,200
Baoluo rice noodles.

18
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:48,640
Come on, Baoluo rice noodles again?

19
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:51,000
What's your relationship with the boss there?

20
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,000
It's breakfast.

21
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,600
I just want to say,

22
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,520
can we not have Baoluo rice noodles every time?

23
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,960
We need to change things up occasionally, right?

24
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,680
Okay, Yu. Tell me next time

25
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,480
what you want to eat,

26
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,400
and I'll buy it for you.

27
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,480
