40
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:33,960
I'll pay you back later.

41
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,079
Okay, Yu.

42
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,880
Noodles 6 yuan/

43
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,800
135.

44
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,560
