59
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,520
I'll wait as long as it takes.

60
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,400
Bye.

61
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,329
See you tonight.

62
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,520
Are you up for this?

63
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,120
You still haven't fixed

64
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,380
