76
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,880
Chao, I was wrong, Chao.

77
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,600
Don't go.

78
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,520
Leaving.

79
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,280
Bye.

80
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,720
