85
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,760
Li Weihao.

86
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,800
Sorry about that.

87
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,800
He's a friend of mine.

88
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,880
Okay, okay.

89
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,970
Why are you here?

90
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,320
I was just passing by,

91
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:23,360
