97
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,800
Let's go to the cafe next door.

98
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,600
Sure.

99
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:48,880
How is your internship at the TV station going?

100
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,120
Not bad.

101
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:51,960
Right,

102
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,680
