105
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,080
Alright.

106
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,040
I'm counting on you then.

107
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,240
I still have work at the station,

108
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,440
