118
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,560
What do you mean?

119
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,320
I like you.

120
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:58,680
No.

121
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,640
Are we that close?

122
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,560
If I remember correctly,

123
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:09,200
