124
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,680
we've met

125
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,880
less than five times.

126
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,720
I...

127
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,400
I also think maybe

128
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:19,200
saying this is a bit sudden for you.

129
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,560
But actually,

130
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,600
these words

131
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,440
have been buried in my heart for 12 years.

132
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,640
Do you remember?

133
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,960
The first time I saw you,

134
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,200
I was captivated by you.

135
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,800
It was at your 10th birthday.

136
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,480
Deeply infatuated.

137
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,160
I'm sorry.

138
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:32,960
I don't remember.

139
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,330
I suggest you forget it too.

140
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,240
You're not my type.

141
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,720
It wasn't before,

142
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,320
