143
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,370
Don't waste your time on me.

144
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,280
I know.

145
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,000
Bai Qiu.

146
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,200
I'm sorry.

147
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,680
I'm sorry.

148
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,280
Hello,

149
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,120
Fu.

150
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,120
Li Weihao,

151
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,640
