164
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,480
Sorry, sorry.

165
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,840
Seriously, be careful.

166
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,200
Li Weihao,

167
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,600
