168
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,320
Where are you?

169
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,450
I'll be right there.

170
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,680
You must be tired.

171
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,730
Have some water.

172
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,280
If he doesn't drink it, I will. Give it to me.

173
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,060
Did you drop out of school?

174
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,220
How do you know?

175
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,530
I saw you doing the paperwork that day.

176
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,720
Keep your mouth shut.

177
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,640
Don't go around talking nonsense.

178
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,880
I won't say anything.

179
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,280
I'm just curious about you.

180
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,080
It's so hard to get into Qiong University.

181
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,210
Why did you drop out?

182
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:21,040
When you have serious business in the future,

183
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,770
you'll naturally understand.

184
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,880
Don't talk so much nonsense to me every day.

185
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:25,720
For my future matters,

186
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,720
I still rely on our young master Lin.

187
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,600
Are you tired?

188
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,200
Have some water.

189
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,610
I'll get going then.

190
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,880
Where are you going?

191
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:45,140
None of your business.

192
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,300
Forget it if you won't tell me.

193
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,580
Where are the clothes?

194
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,480
What?

195
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,400
Clothes.

196
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,100
I'll call Li Weihao right now.

197
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,480
Don't rush me.

198
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,800
Don't rush me.

199
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,520
Hello?

200
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,800
Hello, is this Mr. Li Weihao?

201
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,120
Yes, I am Li Weihao.

202
00:11:57,320 --> 00:12:00,400
This is Beijing Yuxi Design Co., Ltd.

203
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:02,800
We are very satisfied with your previous interview results.

204
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:03,400
I'd like to ask,

205
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,480
