206
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,640
I... I can join in July.

207
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,960
No, no, I can join in June.

208
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,520
I can join as soon as I graduate.

209
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,720
I can join right away.

210
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,360
Okay, goodbye.

211
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:21,080
I'm going to Beijing.

212
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:23,800
I'm going to Beijing.

213
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:04,200
Sorry, Jiaming.

214
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,200
I ran into some...

215
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:05,880
Where did you go?

216
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:07,010
Look what time it is.

217
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,400
Sorry, I encountered a situation on the way.

218
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:09,760
So...

219
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,000
Why so many excuses?

220
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:15,920
Boss.

221
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,160
Boss.

222
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,320
It's ruined.

223
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,960
How did this happen?

224
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,040
I ran into some trouble on the way.

225
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,120
I was late. It fell on the ground,

226
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:27,640
so I washed it.

227
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,440
How could you be so careless?

228
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:29,800
I'm sorry.

229
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:30,480
Did you put the takeout

230
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,810
