231
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:32,800
I didn't.

232
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,920
You didn't? Come on.

233
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:34,840
Come here.

234
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,440
Explain it to my boss. Speak.

235
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,920
Look up.

236
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,040
Jiaming, I ran into some trouble on the way.

237
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:43,240
The clothes accidentally fell on the ground.

238
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:45,040
Why are you delivering takeout?

239
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,520
Did I not give you enough money?

240
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:53,640
Answer him.

241
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,120
Go.

242
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:03,320
Are you that short of money?

243
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,380
Then I'll give you these clothes too.

244
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:07,840
Hurry up.

245
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,920
Come get it yourself.

246
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:19,760
I told you to get it.

247
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,360
Jiaming.

248
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,060
I am short of money.

249
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,760
I really need money.

250
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,000
So all these years,

251
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:30,960
I worked desperately,

252
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:32,120
took part-time jobs,

253
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,720
and earned whatever money I could.

254
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,320
But I'm not far from my goal.

255
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,200
From now on,

256
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,820
I want to make money with dignity.

257
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:42,520
So,

258
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,890
this is my last day working for you.

259
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,480
Thank you, Jiaming.

260
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:53,730
And thank you, Afu, for taking care of me all these years.

261
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:54,720
Thank you.

262
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,900
I won't charge for this order.

263
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:05,480
If there is any extra loss,

264
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,600
I will compensate for it.

265
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,330
I'll take the responsibility.

266
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:12,800
Thank you.

267
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,960
Thank you.

268
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,240
Thank you.

269
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,920
Dr. Chen,

270
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,360
I have good news for you.

271
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:54,040
I got a job offer from Beijing.

272
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,760
Really?

273
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:56,560
Congratulations!

274
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:58,040
I knew you could do it.

275
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,480
I also asked about the apartment for you.

276
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,280
The agent said

277
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:03,560
