278
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:06,040
Weihao, you are really lucky.

279
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:07,690
Thank you, Dr. Chen.

280
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,240
But Dr. Chen, I think

281
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,920
the luckiest thing is meeting you.

282
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:12,240
I'm really looking forward to

283
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,570
meeting you in Beijing.

284
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,760
Me too.

285
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:18,520
Dr. Chen, it's time for ward rounds.

286
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:21,440
Weihao, see you in Beijing.

287
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:22,720
See you in Beijing.

288
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,480
Goodbye.

289
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,400
I asked you to get a bowl and chopsticks.

290
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,840
You didn't even wipe the table.

291
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,720
Look at you,

292
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:32,720
still drinking.

293
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,180
Aren't you driving today?

294
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:38,120
What are you laughing at?

295
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:40,480
I'm asking you.

296
00:16:40,920 --> 00:16:42,360
How is my soup?

297
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:44,800
Playing with your phone again.

298
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:48,120
Long legs.

299
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:52,200
If you ask me, this broken pot should have been thrown away long ago.

300
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:54,120
Look at Mr. Bai's smart pot.

301
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,360
I tell you, you don't need to watch it,

302
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:57,560
and the soup it makes is very delicious.

303
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:59,160
Mr. Bai?

304
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,240
Mr. Bai is rich.

305
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,120
Are you rich?

306
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:03,460
Always talking about Mr. Bai.

307
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:06,319
We've been married for so long. Do you have to mock me like this?

308
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:07,000
Let me tell you.

309
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,200
Just wait, sooner or later,

310
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,160
not just a pot,

311
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,599
I will get you a new house.

312
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,800
I pray to God to open his eyes,

313
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,599
and get me a new house quickly.

314
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,400
Open his eyes.

315
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:16,319
You startled me.

316
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,160
Just get out.

317
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,400
Go outside and play.

318
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,000
Why are you so free?

319
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:25,440
Mom, Dad,

320
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,599
I'm back.

321
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:27,720
You're back.

322
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:30,120
Our son is back.

323
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:31,080
Yeah.

324
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,280
Where is Xiaochao?

325
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,160
Didn't he come?

326
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,200
He has something going on.

327
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,130
He's still busy.

328
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,360
He's a senior. He should be busy.

329
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,240
Come on, son.

330
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,160
Your daily dose,

331
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:44,490
the loving herbal medicine your mom made.

332
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,960
You and your mouth.

333
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:49,600
Mom, I had a bite outside,

334
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,080
so don't cook too much.

335
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,440
Just eat.

336
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,200
Why do you care so much?

337
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,320
I'll go back to my room to read first.

338
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:56,650
Okay, I'll call you when the food is ready.

339
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:01,220
Don't you think he's acting weird today?

340
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:03,840
Look at his smile.

341
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:06,440
It reaches from ear to ear.

342
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:08,200
Are you crazy, old woman?

343
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,720
Isn't it good that the kid is happy?

344
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:10,920
Coming back with a long face every day,

345
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,520
is that what makes you happy?

346
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:25,800
Mom.

347
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:28,250
Did you touch my things?

348
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,320
What things?

349
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:30,600
What's wrong?

350
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,480
What's wrong?

351
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:34,840
What?

352
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,640
Where is my bankbook?

353
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,200
I thought it was something serious.

354
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:40,680
I took it.

355
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,280
How did you know my password?

356
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,880
As for your password,

357
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:45,560
it was easy to figure out with a little thought.

358
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:46,640
Exactly. In our house,

359
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,900
what can you possibly hide from your mom?

360
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,760
Take a look.

361
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:59,320
This is the birthday present we got for you.

362
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,560
There's also some pocket money left on it for you.

363
00:19:01,560 --> 00:19:02,480
As for the main chunk, this 100,000 yuan,

364
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:04,080
your mom bought you this.

365
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:05,160
Lin Group.

366
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,520
That's where Dad works.

367
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,160
This Lin Group

368
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:10,160
is the biggest company here in Qiongzhou.

369
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:10,800
Let me tell you,

370
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:12,240
you really have to praise your dad this time.

371
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,200
I must praise you.

372
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:15,000
You provided the information just in time.

373
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:15,800
It's all thanks to you.

374
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:16,960
But I went to the bank

375
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:18,160
and waited in line for six hours.

376
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,480
Why didn't you go help me?

377
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,010
You told me to watch the pot.

378
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,880
Son, you might not know about this.

379
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,360
Don't look here, look at the front.

380
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:26,800
Let me explain it to you carefully.

381
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,320
Look.

382
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:28,320
Look at this.

383
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,720
See this interest rate?

384
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,440
Look, the annual interest rate is still rising,

385
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,360
it varies,

386
00:19:33,360 --> 00:19:34,490
and pays dividends.

387
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:36,400
Isn't it great?

388
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,560
It's for you.

389
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:43,120
Thanks, Jiaming.

390
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:01,040
Your mom is a technical expert.

391
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:02,120
I didn't even know this.

392
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:02,920
Your mom is the best.

393
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,040
You know nothing.

394
00:20:04,040 --> 00:20:06,100
You're right to leave the money to me.

395
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,320
But son, I'm quite curious.

396
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:02,840
How did you save up so much money

397
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:04,240
without telling your dad and me?

398
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:05,360
Did you want to

399
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,600
Xiaohao.

400
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:10,560
Weihao.

401
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,280
Weihao.

402
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:13,720
This kid.

403
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:14,800
Son,

404
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:16,260
stand right there.

405
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:23,520
Come here.

406
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:24,440
Come.

407
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,400
Let's sit and talk.

408
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:29,480
Hurry up and sit down.

409
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,240
Come on.

410
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,360
Let's have a talk.

411
00:21:33,320 --> 00:21:33,880
You brat.

412
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,960
You really have grown up.

413
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:36,090
Are you still angry?

414
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:37,960
It's just 100,000 yuan.

415
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:39,090
What's the big deal?

416
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,970
Your mom doesn't even know.

417
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:42,130
All these years,

418
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:44,360
I've been paving the way for you.

419
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,640
With the money I've saved up now,

420
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:48,800
even if you can't find a job after graduation,

421
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:50,600
you have nothing to worry about.

422
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:56,410
Does this money have anything to do with those girls?

423
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,080
How did you know?

424
00:22:03,080 --> 00:22:04,810
Where did you take those girls?

425
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:09,370
That has nothing to do with you.

426
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:15,320
I know even if you don't tell me.

427
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:16,980
I don't want your dirty money.

428
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:21,160
I think you've studied so much you've gone stupid.

429
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:22,520
You don't understand it now,

430
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:24,720
but you will once you step into society.

431
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:26,820
If I don't find ways to make money now,

432
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:29,400
just relying on my fixed salary as a driver,

433
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:32,260
our family will never turn things around, you know?

434
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,000
You really disgust me.

435
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:38,480
Dad, when did you become like this?

436
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,280
You...

437
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,840
You're just a loser!

438
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,280
Didn't I do all this for you?

439
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:49,000
Your mother's and my lives

440
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,080
are ruined because of you.

441
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:17,400
Get lost.

442
00:23:18,120 --> 00:23:20,120
Don't come back if you have the guts!

443
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:01,210
I don't know if Zhang Chao still remembers

444
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:02,520
our date tonight.

445
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,000
My name is Wu Yu.

446
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:17,800
Li Weihao

447
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,400
is my roommate.

448
00:24:20,520 --> 00:24:22,580
We've lived together for four years.

449
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,960
He is a very nice person.

450
00:24:26,600 --> 00:24:28,560
He likes to bring us breakfast

451
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:30,480
and clean the dorm.

452
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:33,000
In my memory,

453
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,840
it seems I've never seen

454
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,080
him look sad.

455
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,800
He's always smiling.

456
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,840
Even if they always made me do

457
00:24:43,840 --> 00:24:45,300
things I didn't want to do,

458
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:48,000
even if they often asked me to bring breakfast

459
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:49,160
but never paid me back,

460
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,490
I would think to myself,

461
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:52,000
maybe they're too busy

462
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:52,840
and forgot.

463
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,480
Actually,

464
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,040
rather than being angry,

465
00:24:58,360 --> 00:24:59,640
I was more afraid.

466
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,500
I'm afraid of being alone.

467
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,160
I'm also afraid

468
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:07,000
of not getting along with everyone.

469
00:25:13,040 --> 00:25:14,640
My relationship with him?

470
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,320
He is my best friend.

471
00:25:17,120 --> 00:25:18,650
I wouldn't call us friends.

472
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:21,120
When we were ten,

473
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:22,850
we were just neighbors.

474
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:24,280
Then he moved away.

475
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,960
But I still remember everything from the past.

476
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,440
The things from the past,

477
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,280
I've mostly forgotten them.

478
00:25:32,320 --> 00:25:33,240
Besides,

479
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:36,200
there's nothing in my memory

480
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:38,260
worth reminiscing about.

481
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,520
That was the happiest time of my life.

482
00:25:43,040 --> 00:25:44,560
When I met him again in college,

483
00:25:44,560 --> 00:25:45,490
I was very happy.

484
00:25:46,120 --> 00:25:47,320
I don't know why

485
00:25:48,360 --> 00:25:50,040
he always wanted to be friends with me.

486
00:25:50,040 --> 00:25:51,760
There's no rule that says

487
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:53,440
childhood playmates

488
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:55,570
have to stay together forever, right?

489
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:01,240
L-Later I found out

490
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,120
he changed.

491
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,560
He became very cold.

492
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,440
I don't have this kind of friend.

493
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:14,250
Always looking like he's trying to please everyone.

494
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:16,000
When he gets bullied,

495
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:19,720
he just takes it.

496
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,640
Bullied?

497
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:24,680
There's no such thing.

498
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,440
Boys playing together,

499
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:28,440
isn't it normal to roughhouse a bit?

500
00:26:29,040 --> 00:26:30,240
They often hit me

501
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:33,040
and strip me naked.

502
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:35,920
At most, we just had him run errands.

503
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,720
Our boss paid him.

504
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,880
I really need money.

505
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,860
I want to go to Beijing.

506
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:44,720
So I

507
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,320
followed your advice

508
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:48,120
to look at it from another angle.

509
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:49,560
I just

510
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:50,760
told myself

511
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:52,120
Jiaming is helping me.

512
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:55,520
We grew up together.

513
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:57,000
If he's in trouble,

514
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,460
I definitely have to help.

515
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,000
Do you know

516
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:03,160
what kind of help he needs the most?

517
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:06,800
He needs the most practical help.

518
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:07,680
Money.

519
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,170
Understand?

520
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,810
Is it wrong for me to give him money?

521
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:21,080
He is indeed helping me.

522
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:22,840
It's just that

523
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:24,520
this help

524
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,380
is a bit hard to endure.

525
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,480
But it's okay.

526
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:32,180
It will pass if I just tough it out.

527
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,400
Every time I see her,

528
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,240
I forget all my troubles.

529
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:45,020
Even though he's my brother's driver's son,

530
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:47,450
we're not actually very close.

531
00:27:48,840 --> 00:27:50,640
On her 10th birthday,

532
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:52,280
the first time I saw her,

533
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:53,880
I was mesmerized by her.

534
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,440
At school,

535
00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:57,900
we were just nodding acquaintances.

536
00:27:59,120 --> 00:28:00,600
When she asked me out

537
00:28:00,600 --> 00:28:01,960
for coffee at school,

538
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,120
I was really happy.

539
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:06,760
I asked for his help

540
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:08,290
with some private matters,

541
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:11,610
but I didn't expect him to misunderstand.

542
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,840
He confessed

543
00:28:12,840 --> 00:28:13,900
his feelings to me.

544
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,450
Actually, she didn't know.

545
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:18,320
For a while,

546
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:21,720
I wanted to die every single day.

547
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,320
She basically saved my life.

548
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,330
I didn't know it was his birthday that day.

549
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,720
And I said some very hurtful things.

550
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:36,040
I am truly sorry.

551
00:28:37,800 --> 00:28:39,730
The ones who should be apologizing

552
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:41,240
are them.

553
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,060
How should I put it?

554
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:47,880
Growing up,

555
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:50,000
we couldn't even bear

556
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:51,440
to lay a finger on him.

557
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,440
To take care of him,

558
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,920
I even quit my job.

559
00:28:56,560 --> 00:28:58,960
I was afraid something might happen to him,

560
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,760
afraid he'd get hurt.

561
00:29:01,120 --> 00:29:02,320
Xiaohao

562
00:29:02,320 --> 00:29:03,450
was born premature.

563
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:06,040
He got sick easily since childhood.

564
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,680
To build up his health, his mom

565
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:11,240
didn't even have time for breakfast

566
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:13,600
before going to the market to buy him the freshest fish.

567
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:15,280
I don't like eating fish.

568
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:19,780
I couldn't even bear to drink a glass of milk myself.

569
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:23,320
But things like calcium pills, fish oil,

570
00:29:23,320 --> 00:29:24,720
and lutein,

571
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:26,240
from childhood,

572
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:27,560
he never stopped taking them.

573
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:29,560
I hate taking medicine the most.

574
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,400
Depression?

575
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,600
That's impossible.

576
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:36,130
Xiaohao has been very obedient since childhood.

577
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,160
He never even

578
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:39,200
went through a rebellious phase.

579
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,360
In our family,

580
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,540
there is no resistance at all.

581
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:45,880
Whenever I had any thoughts,

582
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:48,080
they'd use various methods to make me yield,

583
00:29:48,080 --> 00:29:49,040
to make me obey.

584
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:50,920
When he went to college

585
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,080
and left home,

586
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:55,120
every night,

587
00:29:55,120 --> 00:29:57,520
I had to take sleeping pills,

588
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:59,280
or I couldn't sleep.

589
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:01,760
To keep me in Qiongzhou,

590
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:02,920
they even went to

591
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:04,920
the academic affairs office to secretly change my application.

592
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:07,000
I really can't figure it out.

593
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,560
We love him so much,

594
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:10,680
how could he get depression?

595
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:12,880
They love me so much.

596
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,080
Why...

597
00:30:14,080 --> 00:30:15,880
why can't I feel

598
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:17,560
even a tiny bit of love?

599
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:25,400
He's just a coward.

600
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:27,340
He's usually quite cheerful.

601
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:29,160
He's never been depressed.

602
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,240
He's fun.

603
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,760
He's very well-behaved.

604
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:33,120
He's just stubborn.

605
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:34,320
So cowardly.

606
00:31:03,120 --> 00:31:03,960
Ms. Chen.

607
00:31:05,880 --> 00:31:07,280
I just don't understand.

608
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:08,920
Why?

609
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,600
Why do my parents

610
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:12,920
always force me to do things I don't like?

611
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,840
Why does my best friend

612
00:31:15,840 --> 00:31:17,400
hate me so much?

613
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:19,920
Why did the person closest to me

614
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,040
turn into a demon?

615
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:25,400
Why does the girl I like the most

616
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,240
hate me so much?

617
00:31:27,560 --> 00:31:30,120
Why does my best childhood friend

618
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:31,760
want to stay away from me?

619
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:32,800
Just why?

620
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:35,640
No matter what I do, I can't satisfy everyone.

621
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:36,880
Why?

622
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,480
Am I too greedy?

623
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:39,680
No.

624
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:42,240
It's not your fault.

625
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,560
I've tried my best.

626
00:31:44,560 --> 00:31:45,880
I've worked hard.

627
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:47,600
I know.

628
00:31:48,800 --> 00:31:49,800
I know.

629
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:52,040
But it seems there's no way out.

630
00:31:52,040 --> 00:31:53,400
I can't do it anymore.

631
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,400
I'm sorry.

632
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,880
I failed to protect you.

633
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,000
Ms. Chen,

634
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:16,820
you are my confidante.

635
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,120
But I want to say,

636
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:24,920
I'm really tired.

637
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:29,280
I'm really tired.

638
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,520
Xiaohao.

639
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:58,440
Ms. Chen.

640
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,840
I'm going to Beijing.

641
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,520
I will start my new life.

642
00:33:05,080 --> 00:33:06,480
When you see me,

643
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:10,290
you will definitely be very happy.

644
00:33:11,080 --> 00:33:13,410
Haven't you already rented a place for me?

645
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,240
When the time comes,

646
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:17,240
I can just move in.

647
00:33:18,240 --> 00:33:19,920
On weekends, after you get off work,

648
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:21,580
you can take me out for dinner.

649
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:26,080
I've saved up 100,000 yuan.

650
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,940
And I got my admission letter too.

651
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,640
I'm going to Beijing.

652
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:33,240
Ms. Chen,

653
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,160
my confidante.
